{
  "stem": "15732.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What the Haganah did were they bought that ship.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They wanted-- until that particular date, '47, there were-- the Aliyah Bet was only in very small groups, 1,000, 1,500, small ships that were bought somehow and hoped to break through to-- to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But then the political situation was such that it heated up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Before the Jews wanted that the English would give up the mandate an so on, so they decided it wants a bigger ship.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so they decided a ship for 4,500 people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The ship was not big.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But what they did, they took out everything inside and they made bunkers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But the bunkers were so-- the bunks were so near one to another that it was really like a sardine you are there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My father slid in and immediately got a heart attack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He didn't have any strength.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- so my father was the first in this so-called hospital of the-- of the ship.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What was the hospital?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was one very small room that had one bed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was somebody who understood I think very little of medicine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But at least my father had breathing space.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So what we ended up was that my mother and myself were standing all time next to him, because we looked after him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we didn't have to be in the bunk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Shmuelik was-- took on a job of being the one that takes care of the people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a rotation of people to come on the deck to breathe, because it was impossible to breathe down there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So Shmuelik was the one that let people through and organized to go, so he had a little bit of breathing ability, a bit of air too.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
